title: Peanutty Pork and Jumbo Shrimp Yakisoba-Style Noodles with Sweet Chilli and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: Double the protein and double the fun with this yakisoba-inspired noodle dish! Sweet chili-roasted pork tenderloin slices and jumbo shrimp are the stars, but the saucy and buttery veggie-blasted noodles are giving nothing but main character energy in tonight's dinner!
